<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.9">
<l>nāṭṭiṉā yeṉṉai yuṉakkumuṉ toṇṭāka</l>
<l>māṭṭiṉē ṉattaṉaiyē koṇṭeṉval viṉaiyai</l>
<l>pāṭṭiṉā luṉṉaiyeṉ neñcat tiruntamai</l>
<l>kāṭṭiṉāy kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>First, you established me as your servant;</l>
<l>Obtaining that much, I removed my harsh fate.</l>
<l>Through [my] songs, you reveal yourself being in my heart,</l>
<l>Lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
